imageWithCaptionShape.text:
The magic of Christmas is back at Everyman, along with our gift cards and memberships. Give someone (or yourself) the gift of a year of cinema. Stuck for ideas? Our themed gift cards also make perfect stocking fillers.

If you’re after nostalgic throwbacks and 35mm favourites, join us at Screen on the Green for our festive takeover: Christmas on the Green.

messages.widget.accessibility-info.displayed-mess:
We believe that {theaterName} site should be accessible to all people and comply with the requirements of the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines.

Embracing these standards is an ongoing effort. We are committed to improve our site to meet the WCAG 2.1 AA guidelines. If you have questions about its compliance or need help with its processes, please contact us.
